│ This is placed right after matching the two `icmp` instructions. This blanket-disables any inversion check if either compare │
│ has `samesign`.                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ Let's analyze the failing test cases from `select-cmp.ll`:                                                                   │
│ 1.  `@test_select_inverse_samesign_both`:                                                                                    │
